mxTextCell.label:
Defender Katana Upgrade path:
- There are 5 levels for Defender Katana weapon
- Each level upgrade requires one material and a sum of gold
- Scales can be obtained from hunting certain monsters, a commendation is received when completing a special quest
- After hunting each monster the player is able to carve its body 3 times. Each carving has a chance to drop a random material
- When reaching max weapon level the diagram stops
